original: Kindahl, Nils Fredrik, direktör, Norrköping, f. 8/1/Ö2 i Norr köp. av fabr. E. K. o. Fredrika Wirström. G. 1. m. Madeleine Assribekoff; 2. m. Dagmar Nordenfelt. Barn: (i föreg. äkt.) Christer f. 34. — Stud:ex., dipl. fr, Écoile de’s Hautes Études Comimer-ciales i Paris. Anst. i Tyskl. 24, i Engl. 25-26, inneh. av A-B John A. Thulin & Co. i Norrköp. Led. av ’Styr. f. A-B Sv. Hand :banken’S avd :kont. i Norrköp.
translated: Kindahl, Nils Fredrik, director, Norrköping, b. 8/1/Ö2 in Norrköp. to factory owner E.K. and Fredrika Wirström. Married 1st with Madeleine Assribekoff in 19xx. Married 2nd with Dagmar Nordenfelt. Children: (from previous marriage) Christer b. 1934. — Studied for a diploma at the École des Hautes Études Commerciales in Paris. Employed in Germany in 1924, in England from 1925-1926, and currently holding a position at A-B John A. Thulin & Co. in Norrköping. Member of the board of directors for A-B Swedish Hand Bank's local branch in Norrköping.
